{"tid":130680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英發聲明：《蘋果日報》報道失實","createTime":"2017-02-22T14:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T23:42:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41b293fe289936c14a71dc10952da537743b304e","tid":130680,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官梁振英發聲明指，《蘋果日報》有關他或觸犯公職人員行為失當報道失實。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》在星期二刊出一篇題為「政協副主席不獲豁免起訴」的報道。文章引述廉署前總調查主任查錫我指，梁振英有可能因UGL事件而觸犯公職人員行為失當罪行。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英點名批評《蘋果日報》報道內容失實，嚴重影響他本人聲譽，並保留一切追究權利。他澄清他與UGL簽訂離職協議時，並非戴德梁行的董事，而戴德梁行管理層也知悉事件，他本人未曾出任UGL董事，也從沒有參與香港鐵路和UGL之間的商業決定，有關申報問題也已經作交代。"},{"pid":"2a13fba1ed747b3913b1106a1b2590d5741e84db","tid":130680,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=211677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D211677&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8529tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d94f6a7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D211677&h=3d53ee9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=211677</a>"},{"pid":"a40863d45df085de262216c5678f192edb76ef1b","tid":130680,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"佢真係好拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54ae7dc17e50603984e26cf2982b96dfefeb22f","tid":130680,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"見到貪曾俾人判20個月,佢即刻淆底淆到仆街要出聲明屌毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c5beecce5f9dfef4ec9ef2511db7578151e78b","tid":130680,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"此地無銀三百兩"},{"pid":"a97676405b602605223a52a8a84a2f5fe2d1f560","tid":130680,"uid":79201